agement_ht3-300x148.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"148\" /><img src=\"/english/images/organizational_management_ht3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"760\" />\r\n\r\nUser management:\r\n\r\n<img src=\"/english/images/user_management_ht3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"760\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-325\" src=\"http://test.milettech.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/user_management_ht3-300x148.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"148\" />\r\n\r\nAs each enterprise has different business model and management style , the Enterprise Information Management System may need to be customized. Our development tools provide customized system without writing code. Process design:\r\n\r\n<img src=\"/english/images/process_design_ht3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"760\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-324\" src=\"http://test.milettech.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/process_design_ht3-300x163.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"163\" />\r\n\r\nForm design:\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-323\" src=\"http://test.milettech.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/form_design_ht3-300x163.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"163\" /><img src=\"/english/images/form_design_ht3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"760\" />\r\n\r\nModule design: All kinds of queries and menu sequence can be customized without writing code simply querying and configurating XML, convenient and quick.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"/english/images/module_design_ht3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"760\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-322\" src=\"http://test.milettech.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/module_design_ht3-300x81.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"81\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--\r\nif $parrentid==65\r\n<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"showcomment(\'comment/{$commentid}.htm\',\'{$commentid}\');\">Customer Comment</a>\r\n<div id=\"{$commentid}\"></div>\r\n{/if\r\n-->\r\n\r\n</div>','Enterprise Information Management','','inherit','closed','closed','','287-revision-v1','','','2018-02-28 17:06:50','2018-02-2